title: version 1.4.1/Fixed zooming and scaling for playback renderer.
message:
version 1.4.1/Fixed zooming and scaling for playback renderer.
-Created BYBGlUtils-->static gl helpers
-Fixed files sorting on RecordingsFragment. Now the newest is the topmost.
-AudioService. added getPlaybackProgress method.
-PlaybackThread now notifies using frames onProgress callback.
-BaseRenderer. Now handles correcly zooming and scaling when on playback pause. zooms over the point that is being zoomed. Now has a better response for scrolling.
-TwoDimensionScaleGestureDetector-> removed constraint on scaling for small spans. It was making an ugly jump, and "not responding" when scaling begun.

title: Several changes/fixes, mostly on the analysis processing/rendering.
message:
Several changes/fixes, mostly on the analysis processing/rendering.
-analysis layout: added waiting view and made title and back button visible.
-added alert when trying to run an analysis before having done "find spikes".
-Create TouchGLSurface class to handle in a better way the the touches from in the analysis views.
-Corrected back button handling.
-Fixed fragments pushing and popping to avoid excesive number of fragments in the backstack, trying to reuse the already available ones whenever possible.
-Correctly setting analysis renderers and updating these when the analysis has finishesd
-AudioTrack rewinds once playback ends, so to be able to play once again.
-Fixed PlaybackUI update when changing playback to new file.
